title: Slyder (Original)
description: This is the original version of Slyder (i.e. not Super Slyder). It took some doing to find this version of Slyder, but now that I have it, it's not cracked. I can't find any existing cracks for this, so I'd appreciate it if someone who downloads this cracks it and provides a link to the crack in the comments. Then, I'll change this to include the crack.
